Description: BW LPG Limited is Singapore-based investment holding company. The principal activities of Company and its subsidiaries include ownership and operation of liquefied petroleum gases (LPG) vessels, owning and operating Very Large Gas Carriers (VLGC). The Companys operating segments include Very Large Gas Carriers (VLGCs) and Product Services. The Companys VLGCs fleets include BW Mindoro, BW Malacca, BW Magellan, BW Frigg, BW Freyja, BW Volans, BW Brage, BW Tucana, BW Var, BW Njord, BW Balder, BW Orion, BW Libra, BW Leo, BW Gemini, BW Carina, BW Aries, BW Niigata, BW Odin, BW Princess, BW Liberty and BW Trader. The Product Services segment provides fully-integrated product delivery service to customers. The Companys chartered / bareboat VLGCs includes BW Yushi, BW Kizoku, Oriental King, BW Messina, BW Kyoto, BW Tokyo, Berge Nantong andBerge Ningbo. The Companys subsidiaries include BW Gas LPG Chartering Pte. Ltd, BW VLGC Pte. Ltd, and BW LPG Pool Pte. Ltd.
